&gt; How are you defining &quot;coupling&quot;?

Significant change[1] in one component mandates change in other component.

&gt; How are you quantifying coupling?

Yep, good question. I am thinking about a &#39;value&#39; derived from the questions:

Does the change of the provider lead to 

- stop the consumer
- reconfigure the consumer
- recompile the consumer
- &#39;refactor&#39; the consumer
- port the consumer implementation (e.g. when going from RMI to DCOM)

Jan


